*gossip-0.11.2 (15 Jun 2006)

  15 Jun 2006; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +gossip-0.11.2.ebuild:
  net-im enters a joint maintainership of this package with the gnome herd,
  authorized by: allanonjl, dang, leonardop. Version bump to 0.11.2; closes
  bugs #128916 and #134911. Ebuild changes thanks to Mikel Olasagasti
  <hey_neken@euskal.org> and Hans de Graaff <hans@degraaff.org>. ~ppc64 and
  ~sparc lost their keywords due to the new dependencies, filed bug #136906.

